1001160.1002622.1000860.1000874.derived=false 1001160.1000851.1000856.1000937.description=All-Weather Floor Mats
The fun of owning an FJ is being able to explore to your heart's content - and no matter where you roam, these all-weather floor mats take on the elements while helping to keep your interior clean.
Carpet Cargo Mat
You shouldn't have to think twice when you load up an FJ. This carpet cargo mat protects against premature wear and helps keep your cargo area looking like new.

To avoid potential interference with pedal operation, do not install a floor mat on top of an existing floor mat. Each mat must be secured with either quarter-turn fasteners or retention hooks (clips). This floor mat was designed specifically for use in this model and model year vehicle and SHOULD NOT be used in any other vehicle. Cargo load and capacity limited by weight and distribution.

Rear Door Storage Net
This convenient rear door storage net extends across your FJ's rear door and features an easy-access, panel-style pocket.
First Aid Kit
Be prepared for life's little emergencies with this handy first aid kit.
